---

<div class="info-strip" id="info">
  <div class="info-item">
    <p class="info-item-label">// Horario</p>
    <p class="info-item-value">Vie · Sáb<br />Noche</p>
    <p class="info-item-sub">Abre al caer la tarde. Cierra cuando toca.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="info-item">
    <p class="info-item-label">// Ubicación</p>
    <p class="info-item-value">Plaza Mayor<br />El Bonillo</p>
    <p class="info-item-sub">Albacete, Castilla-La Mancha</p>
  </div>
  <div class="info-item">
    <p class="info-item-label">// Servicios</p>
    <p class="info-item-value">Copas · Tapas<br />Cañas</p>
    <p class="info-item-sub">Futbolín · Diana · Sonido & luz pro</p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .info-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .info-item {
    background: var(--bg2);
    padding: 48px 40px;
  }
  .info-item-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .info-item-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .info-item-sub {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .info-strip {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
